name: Singh is King T-Shirt
description:
The phrase which has caught the attention of all, from Bollywood film makers to the streets of Punjab. Show off your pride and let everyone know that 'Singh' is truly 'King".

Bespoke exclusive design by Kuly from International Award Winning group RDB. The 'Singh is King' shirt features a shiny metallic print on a the softest, smoothest, best-looking T-shirt available anywhere.

100% Fine Jersey ring spun cotton with Durable rib neckband.

This shirt is slightly fitted (Euro Fit).

Produced By The #1 Desi Clothing Line in the World - DesiWear
